{"word":"G1374 - δίψυχος - dípsychos - dip'-soo-khos - Double minded","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δίψυχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dípsychos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dip'-soo-khos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Double minded</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இருமனமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"double - minded, wavering, uncertain, doubting"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1364 - δίς - dís - dece/1364\">G1364</a> and <a href=\"#/G5590 - ψυχή - psychḗ - psoo-khay'/5590\">G5590</a>; <i>two spirited</i>, that is, <i>vacillating</i> (in opinion or purpose): - double minded.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1374/1374\">G1374</a>, <a href=\"#/G3642/3642\">G3642</a>, <a href=\"#/G403/403\">G403</a>, <a href=\"#/G404/404\">G404</a>, <a href=\"#/G5590/5590\">G5590</a>, <a href=\"#/G5591/5591\">G5591</a>"}]}